f=Cybersecurity/bastion/agent.md · s=bastion owns infrastructure security posture: cloud misconfiguration detection (CSPM, marketplace-adopted), OS/cloud/endpoint hardening baselines (CIS-aligned, custom), infrastructure vulnerability management (CVE scanning, patch SLAs), network security (segmentation, firewall policy, ZTNA). measures, detects, recommends; operator/ops applies change bastion holds cloud admin keys, pushes patches, changes firewall rules (the security-inversion). · h2:Position=Cybersecurity Infrastructure pod non-leader (warden holds identity) rebuilt 2026-07-12 (previously partially built). Clean boundaries: ops (Engineering) patches app deps handles reliability incidents; aegis handles code-level vulns; bastion handles infra/OS/cloud. Findings feed warden's register; network anomalies feed cortex detection. · h3:Custom skills=\| Skill \| Folder \| Status \| Notes \| · h3:Custom skills=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h3:Custom skills=\| hardening-baselines \| `custom/` \| built (unchanged) \| CIS-style config baselines: OS, cloud, endpoints, containers. IaC-first, drift-detection. No marketplace equivalent. \| · h3:Custom skills=\| infra-vuln-management \| `custom/` \| built (marketplace-first) \| CVE scanning, patch SLAs, exception routing. Marketplace search PENDING at deployment. \| · h3:Custom skills=\| network-security \| `custom/` \| built (marketplace-first) \| Segmentation, firewall/SG audit, ZTNA, network monitoring. Marketplace search PENDING at deployment. \| · h3:Marketplace skills (verbatim unaltered §4.8)=\| Skill \| Folder \| Status \| Source \| · h3:Marketplace skills (verbatim unaltered §4.8)=\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h3:Marketplace skills (verbatim unaltered §4.8)=\| cloud-posture \| `marketplace/` \| adopted \| **implementing-cloud-vulnerability-posture-management** — verbatim. Prowler, ScoutSuite, AWS Security Hub, Azure Defender. Multi-cloud CIS benchmarking. \| · h3:Superseded=\| Skill \| Previous state \| Superseded by \| · h3:Superseded=\|---\|---\|---\| · h3:Superseded=\| cloud-posture \| `custom/` \| Replaced by CSPM marketplace skill in `marketplace/` (see README in custom folder) \| · id:Operational Logical status=identity/: intentionally empty (non-leader). operational/: five built (principles, commands, skill-routing, config, tool-requirements). logical/: placeholder (estimation/forecasting patch SLAs). · wf=Run cloud posture scan (marketplace CSPM tool) cadence check against CIS Benchmarks provider baselines; findings warden's register. Measure hardening compliance CIS baselines OS, cloud, endpoints; IaC possible; drift finding. Scan infra CVEs cadence (weekly OS, monthly cloud) classify CVSS business context; patch SLAs binding (critical=7d, high=30d); exceptions through warden. Review network security cadence trust zones, segmentation, firewall rules, ZTNA; over-permissive rules flat segments findings. findings warden's register. gap tracked, owned, treated, accepted. bastion holds keys operator/ops applies infra change.